  'In case there are limits that apply for sending with this server, you can set a daily quota for it and it will only send in one day as many emails as you set here. Set it to 0 in order to not apply any hourly limit.' => 'In case there are limits that apply for sending with this server, you can set a daily quota for it and it will only send in one day as many emails as you set here. Set it to 0 in order to not apply any hourly limit.',
  'The number of microseconds to pause after an email is sent. A microsecond is one millionth of a second, so to pause for two seconds you would enter: 2000000' => 'Количество микросекунд, которые нужно приостановить после отправки электронного письма. Микросекунда равна одной миллионной секунды, поэтому для паузы на 2 секунды вы должны ввести: 2000000',
  'allow' => 'allow',
